; XRAM assembly integration tests.
; Run: sim6502 -s tests/integration/xram_asm.6502 --backend novavm
;
; The fixture is built from tests/integration/asm/xram_runtime.s. It links
; ehbasic/lib/xram.s directly, then BASIC SYS enters the fixture so the same suite
; can run on Avalonia and live Nova hardware.
; The byte install block is intentionally inside each test after pause(): the
; NovaVM runner cold-starts before each test, so suite-level load() is too early.

